Package: oecdr
Type: Package
Title: Minimal OECD SDMX ETL Demo (R CSV + DBI)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Hyungbae", "Cho", email = "bwade9090@gmail.com", role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: A minimal starter package that fetches OECD SDMX REST CSV responses and writes them to a database via DBI (SQLite by default, Postgres optional). Includes testthat tests, GitHub Actions CI, and a sample offline CSV.
